<div class="prose mb-6 prose-indigo dark:prose-invert">
  <p>Use JavaScript similar to the snippet above to render the following live popover. Titles are set via <%= code("data-bs-title") %> and body content is set via <%= code("data-bs-content") %>.</p>
</div>

<div class="rui dark:p-6 dark:rounded-lg">
